metadata.name: Three-breasted Can Save Our Lives
metadata.description:
Our interstellar three-breasted sweetheart in her habitat
-
"Lola's Habitat" collection is composed of a series of non-male characters depicted in their natural habitats by getting rid of the male-dominated environment. Free from the gaze of masculinity, these subjects reflect their own world in a colorful and patterned environment in Lola's Habitat.
